Wahuwa alla_th_ee yursilu a*l*rriy_ah_a bushran bayna yaday ra_h_matihi_h_att_a_i_tha_aqallat sa_ha_ban thiq_a_lan suqn_a_hu libaladin mayyitin faanzaln_a_bihi alm_a_a faakhrajn_a_bihi min kulli a*l*ththamar_a_ti ka_tha_lika nukhriju almawt_a_laAAallakum ta_th_akkaroon*a*
Wa*a*lbaladu a*l*_tt_ayyibu yakhruju nab_a_tuhu bi-i_th_ni rabbihi wa*a*lla_th_ee khabutha l_a_yakhruju ill_a_nakidan ka_tha_lika nu_s_arrifu al-_a_y_a_ti liqawmin yashkuroon*a*
Laqad arsaln_a_noo_h_an il_a_qawmihi faq_a_la y_a_qawmi oAAbudoo All_a_ha m_a_lakum min il_a_hin ghayruhu innee akh_a_fu AAalaykum AAa_tha_ba yawmin AAa_th_eem*in*
