Q_a_la y_a_qawmi laysa bee_d_al_a_latun wal_a_kinnee rasoolun min rabbi alAA_a_lameen*a*
Oballighukum ris_a_l_a_ti rabbee waan_s_a_h_u lakum waaAAlamu mina All_a_hi m_a_l_a_taAAlamoon*a*
