Wa*o*_th_kuroo i_th_jaAAalakum khulaf_a_a min baAAdi AA_a_din wabawwaakum fee al-ar_d_i tattakhi_th_oona min suhoolih_a_qu_s_ooran watan_h_itoona aljib_a_la buyootan fa*o*_th_kuroo_a_l_a_a All_a_hi wal_a_taAAthaw fee al-ar_d_i mufsideen*a*
